data.description: Charming & secluded home sits on the far side of Woodinville, near the Snohomish Valley, min from Duvall, providing access to the Eastside.  Situated on nearly an acre, surrounded by a mature forest of trees, provides ample parking. The serenity of country living.   This home you’ll has “good bones”, Int. fresh paint. New water heater, new garage doors. 3 bed upstairs includes a master w ¾ bath. A full bath compliments the two other spacious bedrooms.  A deck off the kit descends to a private area w a fire pit.  Downstairs has an ample family room with a fireplace, utility room and bonus space.  New roof this year, 2 car garage w third car covered area, Wired for a generator. Ext. painted in'22.  Close to Duvall for shops n restaurants.
